    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01871.005_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">New Britain</name>
                    <date when="1875-04-11">April 11<hi rend="underline">th</hi> 1875</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Friend and Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>As I have just came <choice>
                    <sic>acrost</sic>
                    <corr>across</corr>
                </choice> one of your letter I thought I would write you a few Lines just to let you
                know that I have not <choice>
                    <sic>for goting</sic>
                    <corr>forgotten</corr>
                </choice> you I am enjoying good health as well as my Family. <choice>
                    <sic>Cince</sic>
                    <corr>Since</corr>
                </choice> I last saw you I was Married I have been Married two years to day I have got 
                <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01871.006_large.jpg" type="verso"/> 
                a little boy ten months old<ptr target="n5001c"/> on the 18 of this month and I named him after you so you see I have
                not <choice>
                    <sic>for goting</sic>
                    <corr>forgotten</corr>
                </choice> you How is the times in Washington it has been hard times here but I have
                got through the winter <choice>
                    <sic>allright</sic>
                    <corr>alright</corr>
                </choice>. We have had very cold weather here it has been the coldest winter I ever <choice>
                    <sic>experance</sic>
                    <corr>experience</corr>
                </choice>. Work is very dull here now I am not doing much at <choice>
                    <sic>preasant</sic>
                    <corr>present</corr>
                </choice> how do you get <choice>
                    <sic>alon</sic>
                    <corr>along</corr>
                </choice> out there. I have been away from Brooklyn Two Years next <choice>
                    <sic>fowl</sic>
                    <corr>fall</corr>
                </choice> I was <choice>
                    <sic>throwed</sic>
                    <corr>thrown</corr>
                </choice> out of work in New York with 
                <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.01871.007_large.jpg" type="recto"/> 
                about two Hundred others ten days before the Panic from the American Bank, Note, Co and did not do any thing till
                January 20<hi rend="underline">th</hi> I came to New Britain <choice>
                    <abbr>Conn</abbr>
                    <expan>Connecticut</expan>
                </choice> and I have been here <choice>
                    <sic>cince</sic>
                    <corr>since</corr>
                </choice> I do not like it here I had rather be in the City some where how is <choice>
                    <sic>Buisness</sic>
                    <corr>Business</corr>
                </choice> there if you come on this way I should like to have you come and see me if
                you can not stay more than one day but <hi rend="underline">I would like to have you
                    make</hi> me a <hi rend="underline">good visit</hi> I have got a fine boy I can
                <choice><sic>till</sic><corr>tell</corr></choice> you he is as <choice>
                    <sic>prety</sic>
                    <corr>pretty</corr>
                </choice> as a picture we all send 
                <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.01871.008_large.jpg" type="verso"/> 
                Love I hope you will forgive me for not writing before this</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>from your <choice><sic>Affectinate</sic><corr>Affectionate</corr></choice> Friend &amp;c.</salute>
                <signed>John M Rogers</signed>
                <address>
                    <addrLine>Address John M Rogers</addrLine>
                    <addrLine>New <choice><sic>Brittain</sic><corr>Britain</corr></choice></addrLine>
                    <addrLine>Conn</addrLine>
                </address>
            </closer>
